(1649, 1, '2018-06-22 15:50:41', '2018-06-22 10:20:41', 'Somnath Sengupta worked as a banker for nearly 39 years and was the CFO and a Director on the Board of Axis Bank, one of the largest private sector banks in the country.He now spends a large part of his time in the social sector – an area that deeply interests him. He is also on the Board of a small finance bank and a non-banking financial company.', 'Somnath Sengupta', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'somnath-sengupta', '', '', '2018-06-22 15:50:41', '2018-06-22 10:20:41', '', 0, 'http://192.168.0.224/wp/k-gives/?post_type=trustees&#038;p=1649', 0, 'trustees', '', 0),
