(1653, 1, '2018-06-22 15:54:32', '2018-06-22 10:24:32', 'Vasu Publicity was floated by Mr. Mudit Kumar Bagla in the year 1999 as an advertising agency specialising in print media releases. Mr. Bagla, with his media-savvy mega mind and a decade\'s worth of field experience with Indian Express newspaper prior to starting his own venture, is a valuable addition to the Kolkata Gives Team.', 'Mudit Bagla', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'mudit-bagla', '', '', '2018-06-22 15:57:21', '2018-06-22 10:27:21', '', 0, 'http://192.168.0.224/wp/k-gives/?post_type=trustees&#038;p=1653', 0, 'trustees', '', 0),
