(1656, 1, '2018-06-22 16:01:18', '2018-06-22 10:31:18', 'CEO of Himalaya Paper Company. Himalaya Paper Company is the merchant of paper and Paper Board. It represents Messrs M/s. JK Paper Ltd., M/s Emami Paper Ltd and M/s Trident Limited. Other group companies are involved in manufacturing and export of CI Engineering Products. The group also have a private brand “ROXX” which is one of the leading brand in Houseware and Tabletop business in India and also represents the world famous Japanese brand “Noritake” in India. The Group also deals in LED lights under it’s own registered brand “OPTILUXX”. Mr. Agarwal’s years of expertise and business acumen will help Kolkata Gives scale new heights.', 'Shyam Sunder Agarwal', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'shyam-sunder-agarwal', '', '', '2018-06-22 16:01:18', '2018-06-22 10:31:18', '', 0, 'http://192.168.0.224/wp/k-gives/?post_type=trustees&#038;p=1656', 0, 'trustees', '', 0),
