(1727, 1, '2018-06-25 16:05:43', '2018-06-25 10:35:43', '<img class=\"wp-image-1145 alignleft\" src=\"http://192.168.0.224/wp/k-gives/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/iskon.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"114\" height=\"103\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>ISKCON Food Relief Foundation </strong>provides Midday Meal for the first generation learners, and it provides the children with the right to education. The organisation provides meals to nearly 9,000 children every day in 131 schools under the aegis of the Kolkata Municipal Corporation. The kitchen is equipped with cutting edge appliances that make the process of cooking fast and hygienic.\r\n\r\n<strong>For further information please visit : <a href=\"http://www.annamritakolkata.org/\">http://www.annamritakolkata.org/</a></strong>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'ISKCON Food Relief Foundation', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'iskcon-food-relief-foundation', '', '', '2018-06-25 16:05:43', '2018-06-25 10:35:43', '', 0, 'http://192.168.0.224/wp/k-gives/?post_type=ngo&#038;p=1727', 0, 'ngo', '', 0),
