(1738, 1, '2018-06-25 16:19:22', '2018-06-25 10:49:22', '<img class=\"wp-image-1132 alignleft\" src=\"http://192.168.0.224/wp/k-gives/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/ASED-logo.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"179\" height=\"72\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Association for Social and Environmental Development </strong>aims at raising awareness among the local youth regarding environmental conservation. The organisation undertakes routine afforestation drives, garbage cleaning and composting initiative, studies local plant and animal species, carries out surveys on chemical use in agricultural activities.\r\n\r\n<strong>For further information please visit : <a href=\"http://www.asedkol.org/\">http://www.asedkol.org/</a></strong>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Association for Social and Environmental Development', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'association-for-social-and-environmental-development', '', '', '2018-06-25 16:19:22', '2018-06-25 10:49:22', '', 0, 'http://192.168.0.224/wp/k-gives/?post_type=ngo&#038;p=1738', 0, 'ngo', '', 0),
