(1742, 1, '2018-06-25 16:27:19', '2018-06-25 10:57:19', '<img class=\"wp-image-1128  alignleft\" src=\"http://192.168.0.224/wp/k-gives/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/amitie-trust.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"122\" height=\"122\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Amitie Trust </strong>was set up to provide a platform for sexual minorities, LGBTHIKQ (Lesbian gay Bisexual Transgender Hijra Intersex Koti and Queer), to articulate their realities and challenges leading to societal integration and respect. The organisation is focussed on the improvement in their life quality and standard; it exists to restore their human rights and dignity. Its vision is a world liberated of exploitation, injustice, stigma and discrimination\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Amitie Trust', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'amitie-trust', '', '', '2018-06-25 16:27:19', '2018-06-25 10:57:19', '', 0, 'http://192.168.0.224/wp/k-gives/?post_type=ngo&#038;p=1742', 0, 'ngo', '', 0),
