(1744, 1, '2018-06-25 16:30:43', '2018-06-25 11:00:43', '<img class=\"wp-image-1125 alignleft\" src=\"http://192.168.0.224/wp/k-gives/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/mukti-rehabilitation-centre.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"187\" height=\"118\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Mukti Rehabilitation Centre </strong>was started in 2002. It was set up to address the drug-addiction needs of children to be nursed back to health and the societal mainstream. Mukti enables adults and children with different abilities to come together and have an opportunity for de-addiction along with education on self help skills, communication skills, literacy skills and behavioural modification. Psychiatric support, counselling and therapeutic intervention are also made available to all of them.\r\n\r\n<strong>For further information please visit </strong>:<strong> <a href=\"http://muktirc.in/\">http://muktirc.in/</a></strong>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Mukti Rehabilitation Centre', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'mukti-rehabilitation-centre', '', '', '2018-06-25 16:30:43', '2018-06-25 11:00:43', '', 0, 'http://192.168.0.224/wp/k-gives/?post_type=ngo&#038;p=1744', 0, 'ngo', '', 0),
