(1748, 1, '2018-06-25 16:35:34', '2018-06-25 11:05:34', '<img class=\"wp-image-1121 alignleft\" src=\"http://192.168.0.224/wp/k-gives/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/nature-mates.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"115\" height=\"105\" />\r\n<strong>Nature Mates-Nature Club </strong>keeps a data bank of Kolkata’s biodiversity along with the other part of West Bengal and also North-East region. Rescuing wildlife in distress in different areas of the city and handing them over to the Forest Authority for proper rehabilitation is another regular activity of NM-NC. It promotes bio-diversity gardening as a conservation measure, they uses butterflies as the key species for gardening.\r\n\r\n<strong>For further information please visit : <a href=\"http://naturematesindia.org/\">http://naturematesindia.org/</a></strong>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Nature Mates-Nature Club', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'nature-mates-nature-club', '', '', '2018-06-25 16:35:34', '2018-06-25 11:05:34', '', 0, 'http://192.168.0.224/wp/k-gives/?post_type=ngo&#038;p=1748', 0, 'ngo', '', 0),
