(1760, 1, '2018-06-25 16:54:43', '2018-06-25 11:24:43', '<p class=\"ngoLogo\"><img class=\"wp-image-1094 alignleft\" src=\"http://192.168.0.224/wp/k-gives/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/leprosy-mission.png\" alt=\"\"/></p>\r\n\r\n<strong>The Leprosy Mission Hospital &amp; Purulia Leprosy Home </strong>engages in caring and treating lepers. The Leprosy Mission Hospital, one of few of its kinds in India, it provides complete care for leprosy patients – from diagnosis to treatment to rehabilitation. Initially envisioned as a home in 1988, the organisation turned into a hospital gradually.\r\n\r\n<strong>For further information please visit : <a href=\"http://tlmpurulia.wixsite.com/home\">http://tlmpurulia.wixsite.com/home</a></strong>', 'The Leprosy Mission', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'the-leprosy-mission', '', '', '2018-08-03 16:34:08', '2018-08-03 11:04:08', '', 0, 'http://192.168.0.224/wp/k-gives/?post_type=ngo&#038;p=1760', 0, 'ngo', '', 0),
