(1770, 1, '2018-06-25 17:06:24', '2018-06-25 11:36:24', '<p class=\"ngoLogo\"><img class=\"wp-image-1083 alignleft\" src=\"http://192.168.0.224/wp/k-gives/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/vivekanand-vikas-kendra.jpg\" alt=\"\"/></p>\r\n\r\n<strong>Vivekananda Vikash Kendra</strong> provides primary and secondary level education to the underprivileged, privileged and tribals. The organisation runs two co-education schools in Purulia with state of the art infrastructure. The school provides education to 500 students, and hostel to 150 students. It also conducts awareness programmes regarding education, child abuse and trafficking.', 'VIVEKANAND VIKAS KENDRA', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'vivekanand-vikas-kendra', '', '', '2018-08-03 16:32:01', '2018-08-03 11:02:01', '', 0, 'http://192.168.0.224/wp/k-gives/?post_type=ngo&#038;p=1770', 0, 'ngo', '', 0),
