(1777, 1, '2018-06-25 17:16:17', '2018-06-25 11:46:17', '<p class=\"ngoLogo\"><img class=\"wp-image-1076  alignleft\" src=\"http://192.168.0.224/wp/k-gives/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/aswini.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<strong>Aswini Nagar Charitable and Welfare Society </strong>was started in 1995. The organisation started with about 100 volunteers, engaged one doctor and one oxygen cylinder. It is the only clinic in Bengal open 24 hours, 365 days of the year.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Aswini Nagar Charitable and Welfare Society', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'aswini-nagar-charitable-and-welfare-society', '', '', '2018-08-03 16:30:43', '2018-08-03 11:00:43', '', 0, 'http://192.168.0.224/wp/k-gives/?post_type=ngo&#038;p=1777', 0, 'ngo', '', 0),
