(1783, 1, '2018-06-25 17:20:48', '2018-06-25 11:50:48', '<p class=\"ngoLogo\"><img class=\"wp-image-1069 alignleft\" src=\"http://192.168.0.224/wp/k-gives/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/kadam.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<strong>Kadam</strong> aims to counter rural poverty and reverse the urban migration. As a means to end, it has mobilised resources to strengthen villagers’ preparedness, particularly women. Apart from providing financial aid, it also provides vocational training in dyeing and bakery to low-income groups in rural areas.\r\n\r\n<strong>For further information please visit : <a href=\"http://www.kadamindia.org/\">http://www.kadamindia.org/</a></strong>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Kadam', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'kadam', '', '', '2018-08-03 16:29:26', '2018-08-03 10:59:26', '', 0, 'http://192.168.0.224/wp/k-gives/?post_type=ngo&#038;p=1783', 0, 'ngo', '', 0),
