(1793, 1, '2018-06-25 17:31:13', '2018-06-25 12:01:13', '<p class=\"ngoLogo\"><img class=\"wp-image-1059 size-medium alignleft\" src=\"http://192.168.0.224/wp/k-gives/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/REACH.png\" alt=\"\"  /></p>\r\n\r\n<strong>Remedial Education Assessment Counselling Handicapped (REACH)</strong> was founded in October, 1980.  REACH has trained numerous specially-abled children and adults different social strata, from urban and rural regions, from within and outside India so that they can lead independent, productive lives.\r\n\r\n<strong>For further information please visit : <a href=\"http://socreachkol.com\">http://socreachkol.com</a></strong>', 'REACH', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'reach', '', '', '2018-08-03 17:23:13', '2018-08-03 11:53:13', '', 0, 'http://192.168.0.224/wp/k-gives/?post_type=ngo&#038;p=1793', 0, 'ngo', '', 0),
