(1904, 1, '2018-08-03 12:33:07', '2018-08-03 07:03:07', '<div class=\"teamHolder\">\r\n<div class=\"trusteeBlue\">\r\n\r\n<img class=\"attachment-medium wp-post-image alignnone\" src=\"http://192.168.0.224/wp/k-gives/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/Sukanya-Bhattacharjee.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"145\" height=\"142\" /><strong>Manager</strong> - <strong>Sukanya Bhattacharjee</strong> comes with experience in the development sector in the key areas of program planning and implementation, resource mobilisation, grant management in CSR. Prior to joining Kolkata Gives she has worked for United Way Mumbai ,The Hans Foundation and GENPACT. She has also gained valuable experience from grass root rural development organizations. Sukanya holds a Masters Degree in Economics. She has a keen interest in the fields of Women Studies and Animal Welfare. Her favorite weekend activities are trekking and camping.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"trusteeYellow\">\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-864\" src=\"http://192.168.0.224/wp/k-gives/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/Srabani-Das-282x300.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"141\" height=\"150\" /><strong>Admin Officer</strong> - <strong>Srabani Das</strong> joins us as Admin Officer. Prior to joining us she has worked for Concern India Foundation for 4.5 years as an Admin Personnel and also for Priya International and SRG (Social Research Group). She is an Arts Graduate from Calcutta University. Her interests are travelling and cooking.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"trusteeBlue\">\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-983 \" src=\"http://192.168.0.224/wp/k-gives/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/FB_IMG_1521100774881.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /><strong>Coordinator</strong> -<strong> Pratik Konthoujam</strong> born and raised in Shillong, Meghalaya.<strong> </strong>Pratik did his schooling from St. Anthony\'s Hr. Sec. School, Shillong and graduated from Gauhati Commerce College, Guwahati. He has a diploma course in Tourism and Hospitality Management. He has worked at Dream Hotel, Kochi, School of Livelihood and Rural Development (SLRD), Shillong​ and freelanced for Deluxe Digital Studios, Bangalore. He loves music, travelling, adventure, and photography.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"trusteeYellow\">\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1159 \" src=\"http://192.168.0.224/wp/k-gives/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/Rajesh-Kumar-1-225x300.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"124\" height=\"165\" /><strong>Accountant</strong> - <strong>Rajesh Das</strong> has seven years of experience in the field of accounts, auditing and taxation, MIS reporting and bank loan management. Rajesh holds an MBA in Finance &amp; System. Prior to joining Kolkata Gives he has worked for Avoru Health &amp; Research Pvt. Ltd., Topsel Toyota, MNR Exports Private Limited , Prolite Paints &amp; Chemicals and Rural Healthcare Foundation.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Team', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '636-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-08-03 12:33:07', '2018-08-03 07:03:07', '', 636, 'http://192.168.0.224/wp/k-gives/636-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
