(2068, 1, '2018-08-20 16:38:20', '2018-08-20 11:08:20', '\r\n\r\n[donate_kgives]\r\n<!--\r\n<div class=\"loginBox\">\r\nThank you for your interest in supporting us. We will ensure that your donations are used to fund those projects run by our associated NGOs, which will benefit the most from these contributions.\r\n<strong>You may contribute to us through the following ways:</strong>\r\n<div class=\"highlight\">\r\n<h5>Cheque/Demand Draft :</h5>\r\nPlease send Cheque / DD in favour of “Kolkata Gives Foundation” along with the Donation Form to the following address:\r\n\r\n34 Alexandra Court,\r\n63 Chowringhee Road,\r\nKolkata-700020, West Bengal, India\r\n\r\n<a class=\"button\" href=\"http://192.168.0.224/wp/k-gives/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/donation_form.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"> Click here for Donation Form</a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"highlight-blue\">\r\n<h5>Account Transfer:</h5>\r\nFor citizens who would like to make an Account Transfer, following are our Account details. Please fill out our Donation Form and email the same to kolkatagives@gmail.com\r\n\r\nBank : HDFC Bank\r\nAccount Number : 50100081872881\r\nRTGS/NEFT IFSC Code : HDFC0000469\r\nMICR Code : 700240024\r\nAccount Branch : 469, Bhowanipore, 88, Chowringhee Road,1st Floor, Next to P.C.Chandra Jewellers, Kolkata- 700020, West Bengal\r\n\r\n<a class=\"button\" href=\"http://192.168.0.224/wp/k-gives/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/donation_form.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"> Click here for Donation Form</a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"highlight\">\r\n<h5>Cash:</h5>\r\nFor citizens who wish to contribute by cash, please email us on kolkatagives@gmail.com with details of the amount you wish to contribute and your address. We will arrange for picking up the cash from your specified address.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>-->', 'Donate to Kolkata Gives', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '27-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-08-20 16:38:20', '2018-08-20 11:08:20', '', 27, 'http://